Package: narrator
Title: Create Natural Language Text Narratives from the Data
Version: 0.0.1
Authors@R: 
    person(
        given = "Denis", 
        family = "Abdullin", 
        email = "denisabdullincz@gmail.com", 
        role = c("aut", "cre")
        )
Description: Template-based NLG system that converts a data frame to text. 
    Different narrative types are available depending on the data frame structure.
    Templates are built with the 'glue' package.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
URL: https://denisabd.github.io/narrator/
BugReports: https://github.com/denisabd/narrator/issues/
